frame.name: Frame
frame.description: Frame used to change your profile background.

wood.name: Wood
wood.description: Log of wood cut by axe. To collect use the `wood` command!

wooden-plank.name: Wooden Plank
wooden-plank.description: Wooden Plank processed by a saw. To create this item use the command `saw`!

coal.name: Coal
coal.description: Piece of coal used to heat the furnace and forge metal bars. Bonus for mining some ores with the command `mine`!

copper-ore.name: Copper Ore
copper-ore.description: Mined copper ore that can be forged in a bar. To collect use the command `mine`!

copper-bar.name: Copper Bar
copper-bar.description: Copper bar forged with ore and a piece of coal. To create use the `forge` command!

iron-ore.name: Iron Ore
iron-ore.description: Mined iron ore that can be forged in a bar. To collect use the command `mine`!

iron-bar.name: Iron Bar
iron-bar.description: Iron bar forged with ore and a piece of coal. To create use the `forge` command!

gold-ore.name: Gold Ore
gold-ore.description: Mined gold ore that can be forged in a bar. To collect use the command `mine`!

gold-bar.name: Gold Bar
gold-bar.description: Gold bar forged with ore and a piece of coal. To create use the `forge` command!

cobalt-ore.name: Cobalt Ore
cobalt-ore.description: Mined cobalt ore that can be forged in a bar. To collect use the command `mine`!

cobalt-bar.name: Cobalt Bar
cobalt-bar.description: Cobalt bar forged with ore and a piece of coal. To create use the `forge` command!

scarecrow.name: Scarecrow
scarecrow.description: A cloth scarecrow that will protect your plantation from bird attacks!

fence.name: Wooden Fence
fence.description: A wooden fence that prevents wild animals from attacking your plantation!

energetic_basic.name: Basic Energetic
energetic_basic.description: A small bottle of energetic that restores some of your energy!

energetic_medium.name: Medium Energetic
energetic_medium.description: A reasonable medium-sized energetic that restores your energy!

energetic_large.name: Large Energetic
energetic_large.description: A great energetic that totally restores your energy!

axe_iron.name: Iron Axe
axe_iron.description: Iron axe for collecting wood! Used with the `wood` command

axe_gold.name: Gold Axe
axe_gold.description: Gold axe for collecting wood! Used with the `wood` command

axe_cobalt.name: Cobalt Axe
axe_cobalt.description: Cobalto axe for collecting wood! Used with the `wood` command

baits_basic.name: Basic Baits
baits_basic.description: Box of baits with common baits to use in your fishing! Used with the `fish` command

baits_medium.name: Medium Baits
baits_medium.description: Bait box with medium baits to use in your fishing! Used with the `fish` command

baits_premium.name: Premium Baits
baits_premium.description: Box with the best baits to use in your fishing! Used with the `fish` command

pickaxe.name: Pickaxe

pickaxe_copper.name: Copper Pickaxe
pickaxe_copper.description: Copper pickaxe for mining and ore collection! Used with the `mine` command

pickaxe_iron.name: Iron Pickaxe

pickaxe_gold.name: Gold Pickaxe

pickaxe_cobalt.name: Cobalt Pickaxe
pickaxe_cobalt.description: Cobalt pickaxe for mining and ore collection! Used with the `mine` command

box_basic.name: Basic Box
box_basic.description: Basic box that will give you with small rewards! Open it using the `box` command

box_common.name: Common Box
box_common.description: Common box that will give you reasonable rewards! Open it using the `box` command

box_uncommon.name: Uncommon Box
box_uncommon.description: Uncommon box that will give you good rewards! Open it using the `box` command

box_rare.name: Rare Box
box_rare.description: Rare box that will give you great rewards! Open it using the `box` command

box_epic.name: Epic Box
box_epic.description: Epic Box that will give you incredible rewards! Open it using the `box` command

fertilizer_basic.name: Basic Fertilizer
fertilizer_basic.description: A basic Fertilizer to help with your harvest, ensures an increase of 5% to 25%!

fertilizer_medium.name: Medium Fertilizer
fertilizer_medium.description: An average fertilizer that ensures a reasonable increase of 15% to 35% in your harvest!

fertilizer_premium.name: Premium Fertilizer
fertilizer_premium.description: The best of Fertilizers, ensures an increase of 25% to 50% in your harvest!

fishing-net_small.name: Small Fishing Net
fishing-net_small.description: A basic fishing net with small size, ensures an improvement of 5% to 10% in your fishing!

fishing-net_medium.name: Medium Fishing Net
fishing-net_medium.description: A reasonable fishing net ensures a 10% to 20% improvement in your fishing!

fishing-net_large.name: Large Fishing Net
fishing-net_large.description: The largest fishing net to catch fish, ensures an improvement of 15% to 30% in your fishing!

bomb_small.name: Small Bomb
bomb_small.description: A small explosive that opens small holes, will help you in your mining ensuring an increase of 5% to 10%!

bomb_medium.name: Medium Bomb
bomb_medium.description: A medium explosive that paves the way through the mine, ensuring an increase of 10% to 15% in your mining!

bomb_large.name: Large Bomb
bomb_large.description: A powerful explosive that will open up large spaces and ensuring a 15% to 25% increase in your mining!
